  "remarks": "Pursuant to paragraph 6 of Security Council Resolution 2371 (2017), paragraph 6 of Security Council Resolution 2375 (2017)and paragraph 12 of Security Council resolution 2321 (2016). DPRK merchant vessel M/V SAM JONG 1 was involved in ship-to-ship transfer operations of oil in late January 2018. Listed as asset of Korea Samjong Shipping (OFSI ID: 13635, UN Reference Number: UN Ref KPe.064)",
